title: Magic/Experience table

properties.name: description
properties.value: This table shows all possible experience sources for Magic in the game, as well as all interactions that require a Magic level. It also lists the items involved in the interactions, as well as other skills involved in processing the item.

content:
This table shows all possible experience sources for Magic in the game, as well as all interactions that require a Magic level. It also lists the items involved in the interactions, as well as other skills involved in processing the item.

Contents

  • 1 Normal spellbook
  • 2 Ancient Magick
  • 3 Lunar spellbook
  • 4 Arceuus spellbook
  • 5 Other experience sources
